{"type": "article", "id": 26418, "title": "张牙舞爪的首饰盒", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-05T07:08:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115050mirwhuae3OqPDjYg.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">这个看上去像是一只张牙舞爪的盒子怪的家饰实际上是英国的 Ana JP Design 设计的一款名为 Buffon 的限量首饰盒，每件均为手工制作并标注号码。除了抽屉，你还可以用它的“手臂”挂东西，既俏皮又富有实用性。售价为 137 美元，你可以在<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/buffoon-jewellery-box-ana-jimenez-palomar-06-16-2015/\">链接</a>中了解更详细的规格。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021150483tEmxXhLdorIFPGc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115048UaP4K6u3jpXlctOT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115049AwjvHEcixy0Wtg32.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115049S4MRXCakh3JFp89B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74969325\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}